usbypass (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
    - Physical USB drive as a password-bypass key for Linux PAM.
    - HMAC-SHA256 handshake bound to USB controller serial.
    - udev hot-plug/unplug hooks, systemd sudo-cache clear on unplug.
    - Interactive TUI, `usbypass verify-now`, `usbypass doctor`.

